在华法国人口述 | 父母第一次中国行，就遇到新冠肺炎疫情……。
At the dictation of a Frenchman in China, his parents encountered a new outbreak of pneumonia at his first trip to China.
黄文菲、金姬。
Huang Wenfei and Jin Ji.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
。
